ce src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3535970/extras/93d1b57c30b883579056bc8cad079c3d.webm?t=1769291233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3535970/extras/93d1b57c30b883579056bc8cad079c3d.mp4?t=1769291233\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a sandalone game in the Lilith Rising universe, events accure some time after the previous games. <br><br>The demon army with thousands of monsters is approaching the kingdom. As the new king, you and your companions must recruit the great viking army to the north to join forces and fend of the immenent attack. On your journey you'll learn more about your mysterious power, and find out about the bigger plot between the gods of hell. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On your adventures you will enjoy the company of the most intriguing companions and learn what it means to be a leader. And... if you play your cards right maybe even find some romance. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A fun fantasy adventure, filled with humor, drama, epic battles, mystery and lots of sex! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3535970/extras/282c9d9c575704003c4461dce2ac10ab.poster.avif?t=1769291233\" width=624 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3535970/extras/282c9d9c575704003c4461dce2ac10ab.webm?t=1769291233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3535970/extras/282c9d9c575704003c4461dce2ac10ab.mp4?t=1769291233\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Valhalla: Lilith Rising is a choice-driven adult Visual Novel featuring: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 5000 of static images and over 140 animations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 7 hours of gameplay with multiple endings. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New sexy love interests</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An engaging mystery </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Original music and SFX </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Two original Songs part of the OST.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plenty of lewd scenes with various girls</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Additional content will be added in future updates.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Save the kingdom from a demon worshiping cult</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3535970/extras/96a74b074018d5474db04be2a6b57d30.poster.avif?t=1769291233\" width=624 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3535970/extras/96a74b074018d5474db04be2a6b57d30.webm?t=1769291233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3535970/extras/96a74b074018d5474db04be2a6b57d30.mp4?t=1769291233\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A grand plot that somehow revolves around you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Date the girl (or girls) of your dreams</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3535970/extras/91c6eae9f289fbd2fa5c8b6124d34b29.avif?t=1769291233\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3535970/extras_big/91c6eae9f289fbd2fa5c8b6124d34b29.avif?t=1769291233 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adventure together with five amazing love int